85
00:08:24,550 --> 00:08:25,550
Hey!

86
00:08:27,710 --> 00:08:30,000
Come out, Malai! Come out!

87
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:31,830
Come out!

88
00:08:38,837 --> 00:08:39,837
Malai.

89
00:08:54,443 --> 00:08:55,443
Sing?

90
00:08:55,703 --> 00:08:57,360
Sing? Sing?

91
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,920
Sing?

92
00:09:07,283 --> 00:09:08,283
Sing?

93
00:09:08,737 --> 00:09:09,737
How are you?

94
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:14,040
Does this mean your amulet to
defeat Malai's ghost...?

95
00:09:15,450 --> 00:09:16,450
Sing?

96
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:22,960
Sing, let go. Sing?

97
00:09:23,543 --> 00:09:25,543
Let go, Sing. Sing!

98
00:09:36,983 --> 00:09:38,796
Ms. Malai, let me go, please.

99
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:33,437
Wait for your husband in hell.

100
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:22,703
I'm asking because the Dark Shadow
House's ghost is very spiteful.

101
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,440
You want her to break your neck?

102
