that my father killed my mother

107
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:45,590
and killed himself.

108
00:11:45,863 --> 00:11:49,560
But there aren't any signs
of struggle at the scene.

109
00:11:51,183 --> 00:11:54,120
- Is it possible they had problems…
- No way.

110
00:11:57,430 --> 00:11:59,080
Ever since I was born,

111
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:03,280
I've never seen my father
hit my mother once.

112
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,080
They never argued.

113
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:08,120
It must have been someone's doing.

114
00:12:09,383 --> 00:12:13,560
I will find out the truth
about what happened.

115
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:24,650
Son,

116
00:12:24,677 --> 00:12:27,520
are you sure you want me to drop
you off at the Dark Shadow House?

117
00:12:28,430 --> 00:12:31,640
Of course. Why would I lie to you?
We've come this far.

118
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,590
Do you really not know

119
00:12:34,057 --> 00:12:36,117
