Smartass bitch.

141
00:13:23,568 --> 00:13:24,568
You bastards!

142
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,120
Take that.

143
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,560
You hit like a girl, you loser!

144
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:34,000
- Mind your business!
- Get him!

145
00:13:34,793 --> 00:13:35,793
Take that!

146
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:38,759
Take that!

147
00:13:39,973 --> 00:13:40,772
- Take that!
- Bring it!

148
