Lieutenant Rat.

162
00:14:59,090 --> 00:15:00,303
Uh, but…

163
00:15:00,409 --> 00:15:01,703
you'd better check on him.

164
00:15:02,296 --> 00:15:04,189
No need. I'm okay.

165
00:15:08,903 --> 00:15:09,903
Ow, hey.

166
00:15:10,583 --> 00:15:11,583
Be gentle.

167
00:15:12,190 --> 00:15:13,457
You whine like a girl.

168
00:15:13,636 --> 00:15:15,800
I got hurt saving you.

169
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:20,150
You didn't save me. There.
It's Lieutenant Rat who did.

170
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:25,673
I'm glad you're both safe.

171
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:28,033
What was that about, Rerai?

172
00:15:28,113 --> 00:15:29,400
I have no idea.

173
00:15:30,046 --> 00:15:31,826
They tried to kidnap me
out of the blue.

174
00:15:31,857 --> 00:15:34,139
But I'd suspect Kla first

175
00:15:34,759 --> 00:15:36,240
because I know his voice.

176
00:15:36,413 --> 00:15:38,286
And out of all my suitors,

177
00:15:38,619 --> 00:15:40,412
he's the most evil one.

178
00:15:41,393 --> 00:15:43,680
And then this guy…

179
00:15:44,099 --> 00:15:46,139
Mai. My name is Mai.

180
00:15:46,819 --> 00:15:49,723
The guy who helped you first
and didn't get your gratitude.

181
00:15:52,139 --> 00:15:54,320
Mr. Mai, what are you
doing out here?

182
00:15:54,433 --> 00:15:56,280
I haven't seen you before.

183
00:15:57,173 --> 00:15:59,280
Can you tell me
where the Dark Shadow House is?

184
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:01,113
How did you know that place?

185
00:16:02,093 --> 00:16:03,959
And why are you going there?

186
00:16:04,686 --> 00:16:05,713
It's my business.

187
00:16:06,186 --> 00:16:07,880
I'm asking because…

188
00:16:09,533 --> 00:16:12,920
because the Dark Shadow
House's ghost is very spiteful.

189
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:14,747
You want her to break your neck?

190
00:16:14,953 --> 00:16:18,446
People who had gone in there
either ended up dead or mad.

191
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:22,100
I don't believe you.
Don't scare me.

192
00:16:22,347 --> 00:16:24,400
- I'm being serious.
- Mr. Mai?

193
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,953
Walk straight that way.

194
00:16:27,093 --> 00:16:28,493
You'll get there after a while.

195
00:16:35,757 --> 00:16:36,944
Thank you, Lieutenant.

196
00:17:00,463 --> 00:17:04,120
I'm asking because the Dark Shadow
House's ghost is very spiteful.

197
00:17:04,343 --> 00:17:06,163
You want her to break your neck?

198
00:17:06,197 --> 00:17:09,690
People who had gone in there
either ended up dead or mad.

199
00:17:10,197 --> 00:17:11,677
It's just a rumor, Mai.

200
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:15,920
You must find out
who killed your parents.

201
00:18:07,570 --> 00:18:08,570
Ow!

202
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:23,203
