our wedding tomorrow.

273
00:32:43,463 --> 00:32:44,463
Of course.

274
00:32:47,423 --> 00:32:48,423
Dech,

275
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:51,023
bring Ms. Malai's suitcase
to the house.

276
00:32:52,037 --> 00:32:53,037
Yes, my lord.

277
00:32:53,683 --> 00:32:54,683
Come on.

278
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:57,830
Watch your step.

279
00:32:57,943 --> 00:32:58,943
Yes.

280
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:02,190
Are you tired?

281
00:33:03,490 --> 00:33:04,490
Not at all.

282
00:33:15,803 --> 00:33:17,240
Welcome, Ms. Malai.

283
00:33:18,762 --> 00:33:20,650
When I found out you were coming,

284
00:33:20,663 --> 00:33:23,763
I came up here
and prepared the room.

285
00:33:23,923 --> 00:33:25,400
Will this do, ma'am?

286
00:33:32,530 --> 00:33:33,723
Of course it will.

287
00:33:36,283 --> 00:33:37,516
Thanks very much, Fueang.

288
00:33:37,750 --> 00:33:39,680
No need to thank me, ma'am.

289
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:41,360
It's my duty.

290
00:33:41,750 --> 00:33:43,650
If you thank me every time,

291
00:33:43,783 --> 00:33:47,110
you'll be thanking me all day.

292
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:52,013
Oh, Fueang, that's okay.
I can do it myself.

293
00:33:52,153 --> 00:33:54,000
You can't possibly do that.

294
00:33:54,507 --> 00:33:58,040
You're here to be
the viscount's wife.

295
00:33:58,413 --> 00:34:01,040
So you'll be another master
of this house.

296
00:34:01,267 --> 00:34:03,267
This is my duty, ma'am.

297
00:34:06,647 --> 00:34:07,647
Or…

298
00:34:09,910 --> 00:34:12,317
are there valuables in it?

299
00:34:12,328 --> 00:34:14,880
If there are,
you can take them out first.

300
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:17,077
- Forgive me.
- There's not.

301
00:34:17,383 --> 00:34:19,960
I don't have many belongings.

302
00:34:20,223 --> 00:34:22,957
There are only
a few outfits in the case.

303
00:34:23,943 --> 00:34:25,943
I just didn't want to bother you.

304
00:34:28,377 --> 00:34:29,560
Ms. Malai,

305
00:34:30,010 --> 00:34:32,040
you're so lovely.

306
00:34:32,603 --> 00:34:34,800
You don't want to bother the help.

307
00:34:36,270 --> 00:34:37,923
- Here.
- That's okay, ma'am.

308
00:34:38,517 --> 00:34:39,640
It's okay, ma'am.

309
00:35:19,850 --> 00:35:23,120
Who is playing
a fiddle at this hour?

310
00:36:52,443 --> 00:36:53,709
And this is…

311
00:36:54,683 --> 00:36:55,823
Ms. Malai,

312
00:36:56,757 --> 00:36:58,160
my bride-to-be.

313
00:37:10,497 --> 00:37:11,704
Why did you stop?

314
00:37:11,817 --> 00:37:13,160
It sounded beautiful.

315
00:37:15,570 --> 00:37:17,840
So sweet I thought
you were in love.

316
00:37:19,637 --> 00:37:21,400
Eh, maybe you are.

317
00:37:22,603 --> 00:37:23,803
Whose daughter?

318
00:37:24,463 --> 00:37:26,320
Want me to tell His Lordship?

319
00:37:26,550 --> 00:37:28,520
Get to your point. Stop yapping.

320
00:37:30,757 --> 00:37:32,360
His Lordship sent for you.

321
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:52,783
May you two have
many children and grandchildren.

322
00:37:53,963 --> 00:37:54,963
Malai!

323
00:37:55,930 --> 00:37:57,097
My name is Bu-nga,

324
00:37:57,463 --> 00:38:00,000
the daughter of
the Eastern Trade Minister.

325
00:38:01,770 --> 00:38:02,920
Release Ms. Malai!

326
00:38:10,863 --> 00:38:11,863
Malai!

327
00:38:13,569 --> 00:38:14,369
Dech!

328
00:38:14,370 --> 00:38:15,910
Who are you to Ms. Malai?

329
00:38:16,069 --> 00:38:17,642
She's His Lordship's wife,

330
00:38:18,082 --> 00:38:19,082
not yours.

331
00:38:19,882 --> 00:38:22,880
From now on, Ramphoei will
live here as my other wife.

332
00:38:25,709 --> 00:38:27,989
Why did you take my floats that
I made a wish on, Dech?

333
00:38:28,177 --> 00:38:30,320
Don't you want
His Lordship to have children?

334
00:38:30,496 --> 00:38:32,636
Evil! You're evil!

335
00:38:49,776 --> 00:38:55,336
♪ Here's a heart
that's always faithful ♪

336
00:38:55,636 --> 00:38:59,760
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

337
00:39:01,302 --> 00:39:07,136
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

338
00:39:07,873 --> 00:39:11,390
♪ To you alone ♪

339
00:39:11,554 --> 00:39:17,360
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

340
00:39:17,607 --> 00:39:23,640
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

341
00:39:24,229 --> 00:39:26,680
♪ Whatever you want ♪

342
00:39:27,116 --> 00:39:31,760
♪ Everything I've done ♪

343
00:39:32,117 --> 00:39:34,400
♪ What's it for? ♪

344
00:39:34,730 --> 00:39:40,080
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

345
00:39:40,422 --> 00:39:45,840
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

346
00:39:46,142 --> 00:39:51,640
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

347
00:39:51,957 --> 00:39:57,720
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪
